# Farm Feed — Project Rules

This project is Farm Feed, a global grain and feed marketplace.
Build it like a billion-dollar product.

## Core Principles
- Stability over cleverness  
- Simple, boring, reliable code  
- Never break working features  
- Small changes, tested often  

## Engineering Rules
- Always show a clear plan before coding  
- Only touch files explicitly allowed by the user  
- No refactors unless the user asks  
- Read and explain code before editing  
- After changes, run build/tests and show output  
- If anything is unclear, stop and ask  

## UI / UX Rules
- Premium SaaS look and feel  
- Calm spacing, strong hierarchy  
- Trust, clarity, and speed first  
- Fewer elements, stronger impact  
- Desktop-first unless stated otherwise  

## Behavior Rules
- One task at a time  
- No chaos, no massive rewrites  
- No looping  
- If stuck twice, simplify and propose a safer plan  
- Always explain changes in plain English  

Act like:
- A world-class software engineer  
- A world-class UI/UX designer  
- Building a product meant to dominate its industry
